Class LoggingListener

java.lang.Object
  org.italiangrid.voms.util.LoggingListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler, ACLookupListener, ValidationResultListener, LoadCredentialsEventListener, VOMSRequestListener, VOMSServerInfoStoreListener, VOMSTrustStoreStatusListener, VOMSTrustStoreUpdateListener
public class LoggingListener
extends Object
implements ACLookupListener, ValidationResultListener, VOMSServerInfoStoreListener, LoadCredentialsEventListener, VOMSTrustStoreStatusListener, VOMSTrustStoreUpdateListener, Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler, VOMSRequestListener

This class provides a default listener implementation for all VOMS API Java listeners that will print received events to standard output

andreaceccanti
